    <h1>Refund Policy</h1>
    <p class="small">Last updated: November 30, 2025</p>

    <p>BuySahi does not sell products directly. All purchases made through BuySahi are completed on Amazon or other third-party seller sites. As such, BuySahi does not handle refunds, returns, cancellations, or shipping issues.</p>

    <h2>1. Refunds &amp; Returns</h2>
    <p>All refunds, returns, and exchanges must be processed according to the seller’s policy — in most cases this is Amazon's Returns &amp; Refunds policy. Please visit Amazon’s help pages from your Amazon orders page for details.</p>

    <h2>2. Damaged or Incorrect Items</h2>
    <p>If you receive a damaged or incorrect item, please contact Amazon Customer Support through your orders page. BuySahi cannot accept returns or process refunds directly.</p>

    <h2>3. Order Cancellations</h2>
    <p>Order cancellations must be made on Amazon. BuySahi cannot cancel orders.</p>

    <h2>4. Affiliate Commission</h2>
    <p>Returned or refunded purchases may result in cancellation of affiliate commission. This does not affect your compensation or refund process with the seller.</p>

    <h2>5. Questions</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about information shown on BuySahi, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@buysahi.in">support@buysahi.in</a>.</p>

